description: Curious about using a 13 month calendar, also known as the International Fixed Calendar (IFC)? Ask Alexa for today's date, and you, too, can use an obscure calendar, just like Kodak employees did for 70 years! (Calendar is a protected word, say "cal" instead)
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask 13 Month Cal for the date
Alexa, ask 13 Month Cal about today's date
Alexa, ask 13 Month Cal what is the date
name: 13 Month Cal
shortDescription: Get today's date on the 13 Month Cal!
